{"tid":770780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(窮撚坐港鐵)邊個設計紅磡站","createTime":"2018-08-07T11:25:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-07T12:21:06.000Z","uid":78318,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5ceb7f6c87b9574e700d22d9d096bc6e9ac29bda","tid":770780,"uid":78318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:25:55.000Z","msg":"點解紅磡站個設計咁痴線<br />\n坐東鐵入去 佢架西鐵一定係另一個平行月台 <br />\n仲要一分鐘就開走<br />\n跑上電梯過去又唔夠時間 <br />\n迫你等五分鐘下一班同一個平行月台既西鐵<br />\n<br />\n試過跑上去過隔離 點知望住架西鐵開走<br />\n死死氣過返原本個月台<br />\n<br />\n個月台又鬼死咁熱<br />\n重點係我屌你老母 <br />\n我好撚趕時間啊仆街:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c225b0634aeb2aaed353416ca933512e8e2ac4","tid":770780,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:28:46.000Z","msg":"過時設計"},{"pid":"4b2e20f6f8b368b2eff56e52549d299177fa70af","tid":770780,"uid":9387,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"咁你都係最多等5分鐘姐<br />\n算係咁啦<br />\n紅磡站最撚垃圾就係好柒熱"},{"pid":"41e801d9b413cdfe08d4d37843f13cb31a6b7954","tid":770780,"uid":36547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:30:30.000Z","msg":"唔係喺對面架咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cee569d0fe16db1b66e79c259c9a3d32aad054","tid":770780,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"小明"},{"pid":"379c24f76f5386b5d49c7774ee1cc66e396355fd","tid":770780,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:32:44.000Z","msg":"直接行過去"},{"pid":"574359680502d1fefc7273591f710a5f710ea21d","tid":770780,"uid":78318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b2e20f6f8b368b2eff56e52549d299177fa70af","tid":770780,"uid":9387,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"咁你都係最多等5分鐘姐<br />\n算係咁啦<br />\n紅磡站最撚垃圾就係好柒熱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T11:58:18.000Z","msg":"問題我好趕時間<img src=\"/a